  "texts": [
    "It may appear paradoxical that we should want AI to resist, if we also want us to align.",
    "Does that not hand it the very same power that we are so afraid to lose?",
    "I think not.",
    "Primarily because power is not a finite resource; it is always in contestation that it manifests, in situations where all parties are free to act otherwise.",
    "It is in the enactment of the possibility to resist that an agent becomes responsible."
  ],
